{"tid":326152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【整容累事？】韓國藝人患癌漸趨年輕化","createTime":"2017-07-17T18:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T09:24:36.000Z","uid":14730,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f46ac75291512f4d9106bbb44d53c25f6e4337","tid":326152,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"過往有不少年輕韓星不幸患癌，如32歲男星崔勝元去年證實患上急性白血病，也一樣暫定手上所有工作，專心接受治療，直至上年年底病情好轉，回家休養及逐漸開始與音樂劇活動。而33歲女諧星安英美亦曾於2007年確診甲狀腺癌，最終都能康復；另一位是諧星劉相務就捲入性侵案獲證清白後，最近證實患上大腸癌第三期，現已接受手術。另一位是女團Jewelry出身的36歲女星朴貞雅，於2013年患上甲狀腺癌，接受手術後，身體已經完全恢復。不過童星出身的女演員李貞後，上年年尾因不敵癌魔，終於32歲，令人唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uBciqn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uBciqn&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJijQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6d55bc18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uBciqn</a>"},{"pid":"61d845e23619b4c50d226e91bf4ab8c0cc234066","tid":326152,"uid":4180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:48:18.000Z","msg":"韓國飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9859849a78c51a33268da527851a43b547d337e8","tid":326152,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓國飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日食公仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ca3dd058b74e1f08098e5d1e7104d082fef5d3","tid":326152,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>韓國飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日食公仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n極邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d37fdc1e8a968973d1134a82006d50f8b0bc4fe","tid":326152,"uid":45213,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"